reviewText: All my family loved these movies. Have watched both twice.
Read the book (The Egg and I), and saw the movie long ago.  A great story!
A big touch of the past loved it!!!
The Egg and I is a book that was written by a woman who moved to my small town on the Olympic Peninsula in WA State.  The movie is a hoot.  Ma and Pa Kettle are a hoot.  Everyone should watch it!
Was a gift they loved it. Great shipping

Surprised to see TWO movies together, I loved the story (again) and
had a ball watching all the nonsense.
realllly  fun  i bought it cause it was on sale.  now i will get the whole series.
Two excellent movies. About love, family and sacrifice. The endings were happy. We enjoyed them immensely.
what a great clean fun movie ..LOVE LOVE ...LOVED IT ..I WISH THEY MADE MOVIES LIKE THIS IN THIS DAY AND AGE....I WILL WATCH THIS OVER AND OVER AGAIN......
